\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\frac{\partial\rho_{11}}{\partial t}=-2\kappa^{\text{3D}}\rho_{00}\rho_{11}\sin^{2}\omega_{0}t.
\end{equation}

\end_inset

We define the Ehrenfest decay rate by 
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{\partial\rho_{11}}{\partial t}=-k_{Eh}\rho_{11}$
\end_inset

