\begin_layout Plain Layout
Cohen Eq.(31) of p.310 is exactly Eq.
 (19) of p.308, so 
\begin_inset Formula $D^{\prime}=\epsilon_{0}E$
\end_inset

.
 so the electric-dipole Hamiltonian Eq.(38) is 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\widehat{H}=\widehat{H}_{s}+\sum_{k}\hbar\omega_{k}\left(\widehat{a}_{k}^{\dagger}\widehat{a}_{k}+\frac{1}{2}\right)-\widehat{\mathbf{P}}\left(0\right)\cdot\widehat{\mathbf{E}}\left(0\right),
\]

